{"tid":2322061,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【陳浩天脫罪指自己隨遇而安「無必要唔走 」 寄語港人「努力生存落去唔好死」】","createTime":"2020-12-12T04:35:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-12T09:30:03.000Z","uid":131691,"like":71,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"e6484ca231eec219ad85d7ff788c408ebf1ca988","tid":2322061,"uid":131691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T04:35:45.000Z","msg":"陳浩天光復上水案，今日在西九龍裁判法院被裁定兩罪不成立。陳離開法院時見記者，指對律政司會否上訴感到樂觀。他又指自己「隨遇而安」，未有離開打算，更寄語在不同地方的香港人「努力生存落去唔好死，大家加油，為著嗰個共同目標一齊奮鬥生存落去。」<br />\n<br />\n陳浩天表示要感謝......<br />\n<br />\n全文（唔po全部因為唔想偷click rate）： <a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=397721834977555&amp;id=109301110486297\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D397721834977555%26id%3D109301110486297&d=Lu%2FYWbP3Pl%2BxzjQ0by0jcrP2tejZlako6KwT%2FyznMNw%3D&h=f5a88bce\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=397721834977555&amp;id=109301110486297</a>"},{"pid":"72ad86656301b63ed5880d2c0619239c7b347090","tid":2322061,"uid":4302,"like":3,"dislike":6,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T04:36:19.000Z","msg":"手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff1af0dad00e7c2975f03748ce946e39c36961c7","tid":2322061,"uid":35301,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T04:36:44.000Z","msg":"堡主<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df474cea1b0036dc8dafe87cd1b5ad89f48e0ead","tid":2322061,"uid":236414,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T04:36:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"620ebaa8c355831d2cc9a789ed16262a8c02bc31","tid":2322061,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-12T04:37:27.000Z","msg":"堡主 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass